rows.label: soul29_P0101
rows.name:
Let's get going!
 Bring it to them!

rows.label: soul29_P0102
rows.name:
Melee attacks!
 Seize the advantage!

rows.label: soul29_P0103
rows.name:
Here we go!
 Close in and attack!

rows.label: soul29_P0201
rows.name: I'll strike first! Attack at range!

rows.label: soul29_P0202
rows.name: It's go-time! Buff me up!

rows.label: soul29_P0203
rows.name:
Be careful! We should
 weaken it!

rows.label: soul29_P0301
rows.name:
Use melee attacks!
 Don't fall behind!

rows.label: soul29_P0302
rows.name: Follow me! Suppressive fire!

rows.label: soul29_P0303
rows.name:
Auras ready! Let's make
 this OUR fight!

rows.label: soul29_P0401
rows.name:
I don't feel so hot...
 Heal me up!

rows.label: soul29_P0402
rows.name:
They're too strong! We need
 more power to win this!

rows.label: soul29_P0403
rows.name:
I'm in a bind here.
 Please help!

rows.label: soul29_P0501
rows.name:
Patch me up! I have to
 stay in this!

rows.label: soul29_P0502
rows.name:
Heal me, would ya?
 I don't wanna die!

rows.label: soul29_P0503
rows.name:
Don't waste time on me.
 Buff up and fight back!

rows.label: soul29_P0601
rows.name:
You have to avenge me...
 Hit 'em where it counts!

rows.label: soul29_P0602
rows.name: It's up to you now...

rows.label: soul29_P0603
rows.name:
Get your auras ready... And
 be more careful than I was...

rows.label: soul29_P0701
rows.name: Nailed it! Now, melee!

rows.label: soul29_P0702
rows.name:
You see that?!
 Attack at range!

rows.label: soul29_P0703
rows.name: Now! Cripple them!

rows.label: soul29_P0801
rows.name:
Bam! Got it!
 Melee attacks next!

rows.label: soul29_P0802
rows.name:
Appendage destroyed!
 Hit 'em again!

rows.label: soul29_P0803
rows.name:
Part demolished!
 Weaken them more!

rows.label: soul29_P0901
rows.name:
We're wearing 'em down!
 Aim for their weak point!

rows.label: soul29_P0902
rows.name:
Just a little further!
 Time to buff up!

rows.label: soul29_P0903
rows.name:
Whaddya say?
 Let's kick 'em around!

rows.label: soul29_P1001
rows.name:
Close in and smash 'em!
 No holds barred!

rows.label: soul29_P1002
rows.name:
Beautiful! Okay, get 'em
 in your sights!

rows.label: soul29_P1003
rows.name:
NOW they're reconsidering!
 Cripple them!

rows.label: soul29_P1101
rows.name:
How about a little change of
 pace? You know what I mean!

rows.label: soul29_P1102
rows.name:
Need a fresh start?
 Use an aura!

rows.label: soul29_P1103
rows.name: Aura ready! Pump us up!

rows.label: soul29_P1201
rows.name: Overclock! Here I go!

rows.label: soul29_P1202
rows.name:
Check this out!
 Suuuper-Overclock!

rows.label: soul29_P1203
rows.name:
Watch this!
 And prep your auras!

rows.label: soul29_C0101
rows.name:
Enemy down!
 Close in on the next one!

rows.label: soul29_C0102
rows.name: I finished one off! Next!

rows.label: soul29_C0103
rows.name:
Don't get cocky. Buff us up
 before we keep going!

rows.label: soul29_C0201
rows.name:
You gotta be light on
 your feet! It's aura time!

rows.label: soul29_C0202
rows.name:
Not even frickin' CLOSE!
 Hook a girl up!

rows.label: soul29_C0203
rows.name:
Whoa! Look out! This loser
 needs a shot in the face!

rows.label: soul29_C0301
rows.name:
You see that?! Step in
 and finish them!

rows.label: soul29_C0302
rows.name:
Aw yeah! I'm lethal!
 Now fire!

rows.label: soul29_C0303
rows.name:
Nice one, if I do say
 so myself. Close in!

rows.label: soul29_C0401
rows.name:
What theâ€” Look at the sky!
 Get powered up!

rows.label: soul29_C0402
rows.name:
This planet's weather just can't
 make up its mind! Use an aura!

rows.label: soul29_C0403
rows.name:
Hmm, in this weather, impairing
 the enemy just might work!

rows.label: soul29_C0501
rows.name:
My legs are about to fall off.
 I need a boost!

rows.label: soul29_C0502
rows.name:
Look at me go! Or better yet,
 buff me up!

rows.label: soul29_C0503
rows.name:
All this running's got
 me fired up!

rows.label: soul29_C0601
rows.name:
Thanks! Now show me how
 you handle that melee weapon!

rows.label: soul29_C0602
rows.name:
Thanks, but don't stop
 shooting on my account!

rows.label: soul29_C0603
rows.name: Saved! Don't forget your aura!

rows.label: soul29_C0701
rows.name:
I owe ya. Let's power
 up and do this!

rows.label: soul29_C0702
rows.name:
That's girl power! Now let's
 take it even further!

rows.label: soul29_C0703
rows.name:
Our auras are WAY better
 than the guys', right?

rows.label: soul29_C0801
rows.name:
I can take it...
 Just stay on them!

rows.label: soul29_C0802
rows.name:
They'll never get me...
 Cover fire, please!

rows.label: soul29_C0803
rows.name:
I'm not running! Buff up
 and push 'em back!

rows.label: soul29_C0901
rows.name:
Fire! I'll keep 'em
 pinned down!

rows.label: soul29_C0902
rows.name:
I'm taking hits from above!
 Keep firing!

rows.label: soul29_C0903
rows.name:
It's all about good positioning.
 Now fire!

rows.label: soul29_C1001
rows.name:
Down ya go, sucker!
 Nail 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1002
rows.name:
Oh, SO sorry.
 Now slaughter 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1003
rows.name: Woohoo! Now cripple 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1101
rows.name:
Ooh! Stunned it!
 Move in and strike!

rows.label: soul29_C1102
rows.name:
Stunned it! They're an
 easy target now!

rows.label: soul29_C1103
rows.name:
They can't move!
 Time to weaken 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1201
rows.name:
Look at this snoozer.
 Give 'em a rude awakening!

rows.label: soul29_C1202
rows.name:
Aw, they're sleeping. Try and
 be quiet when you SHOOT 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1203
rows.name:
Feels a little bad to hit 'em while
 they're asleep, huh? Oh well!

rows.label: soul29_C1301
rows.name:
I'm holding 'em! Melee attacks
 should work great!

rows.label: soul29_C1302
rows.name: Got 'em! Take the shot!

rows.label: soul29_C1303
rows.name:
Stop struggling!
 Somebody hit this freak!

rows.label: soul29_C1401
rows.name:
Patch me up!
 I'm falling apart here!

rows.label: soul29_C1402
rows.name:
I'm a wreck over here! You're
 gonna have to hit 'em for me!

rows.label: soul29_C1403
rows.name:
Hey, leave my Doll alone!
 Guys, shoot them!

rows.label: soul29_C1501
rows.name:
My Doll's busted!
 I should have patched it up.

rows.label: soul29_C1502
rows.name:
Pah, who needs a Doll, anyway?
 Buff me up and let me at 'em!

rows.label: soul29_C1503
rows.name:
I'm just getting started!
 Use your Overclock!

rows.label: soul29_C1601
rows.name:
Low fuel? I hope the next
 re-up will cover me!

rows.label: soul29_C1602
rows.name:
I could really use a refuel!
 Anyone?!

rows.label: soul29_C1603
rows.name:
Oh no! Help!
 I'm running on fumes!
